                  "arguments": "{\"path\": \"/tmp/isolated_workspace_1091/answer.md\", \"content\": \"# 第38届全国中学生物理竞赛复赛试题作答\\n\\n## 一、光学透镜问题\\n\\n### （1）平凸透镜凸面形状\\n\\n由费马原理，平行光入射到透镜后会聚于F点，光程相等。\\n\\n设凸面上任一点P的极坐标为$(r,\\\\theta)$，以O为极点，OF为极轴。\\n\\n平行光从左侧入射，经凸面折射后会聚于F点。\\n\\n光程条件：$nr + (r_0 - r\\\\cos\\\\theta) = nr_0$\\n\\n整理得：$nr - r\\\\cos\\\\theta = nr_0 - r_0$\\n\\n$(n - \\\\cos\\\\theta)r = (n-1)r_0$\\n\\n解得极坐标方程：$r = \\\\frac{(n-1)r_0}{n - \\\\cos\\\\theta}$\\n\\n转换为直角坐标系，取O为原点，OF为x轴正方向：\\n\\n$x = r\\\\cos\\\\theta$，$y = r\\\\sin\\\\theta$，$r = \\\\sqrt{x^2+y^2}$\\n\\n代入得：$\\\\sqrt{x^2+y^2} = \\\\frac{(n-1)r_0}{n - \\\\frac{x}{\\\\sqrt{x^2+y^2}}}$\\n\\n$(n-1)r_0 = n\\\\sqrt{x^2+y^2} - x$\\n\\n$n\\\\sqrt{x^2+y^2} = (n-1)r_0 + x$\\n\\n两边平方：$n^2(x^2+y^2) = (n-1)^2r_0^2 + 2(n-1)r_0 x + x^2$\\n\\n$(n^2-1)x^2 - 2(n-1)r_0 x + n^2y^2 = (n-1)^2r_0^2$\\n\\n$(n-1)(n+1)x^2 - 2(n-1)r_0 x + n^2y^2 = (n-1)^2r_0^2$\\n\\n除以$(n-1)$：$(n+1)x^2 - 2r_0 x + \\\\frac{n^2}{n-1}y^2 = (n-1)r_0^2$\\n\\n配方：$(n+1)\\\\left(x - \\\\frac{r_0}{n+1}\\\\right)^2 + \\\\frac{n^2}{n-1}y^2 = (n-1)r_0^2 + \\\\frac{r_0^2}{n+1}$\\n\\n$(n+1)\\\\left(x - \\\\frac{r_0}{n+1}\\\\right)^2 + \\\\frac{n^2}{n-1}y^2 = \\\\frac{n r_0^2}{n+1}$\\n\\n标准形式：$\\\\frac{\\\\left(x - \\\\frac{r_0}{n+1}\\\\right)^2}{\\\\frac{n r_0^2}{(n+1)^2}} + \\\\frac{y^2}{\\\\frac{(n^2-1)r_0^2}{n^2(n+1)}} = 1$\\n\\n### （2）平凹透镜问题\\n\\n#### （i）凹面形状\\n\\n插入平凹透镜后，汇聚光线经凹面折射后平行射出。\\n\\n设凹面上任一点Q的极坐标为$(r',\\\\theta')$，以F为极点，FO为极轴（向左为正）。\\n\\n从F点发出的光线经凹面折射后平行向右射出。\\n\\n光程条件：$n'r' + r'\\\\cos\\\\theta' = n'r_0'$\\n\\n$(n' + \\\\cos\\\\theta')r' = n'r_0'$\\n\\n解得极坐标方程：$r' = \\\\frac{n'r_0'}{n' + \\\\cos\\\\theta'}$\\n\\n转换为直角坐标系，取F为原点，FO为x轴负方向（即原坐标系中x轴正方向）：\\n\\n在原坐标系中，设凹面方程为$x = x(y)$，F点坐标为$(r_0, 0)$。\\n\\n以F为原点的直角坐标：$X = r_0 - x$，$Y = y$\\n\\n$X = r'\\\\cos\\\\theta'$，$Y = r'\\\\sin\\\\theta'$\\n\\n代入得：$r' = \\\\frac{n'r_0'}{n' + \\\\frac{X}{r'}} = \\\\frac{n'r_0'}{n' + \\\\frac{r_0-x}{r'}}$\\n\\n$r'(n' + \\\\frac{r_0-x}{r'}) = n'r_0'$\\n\\n$n'r' + r_0 - x = n'r_0'$\\n\\n$n'\\\\sqrt{(r_0-x)^2 + y^2} = n'r_0' - r_0 + x$\\n\\n两边平方：$n'^2[(r_0-x)^2 + y^2] = (n'r_0' - r_0 + x)^2$\\n\\n展开整理得双曲线方程。\\n\\n#### （ii）光束半径比\\n\\n入射平行光束半径：$R_{in} = r_0\\\\tan\\\\theta_{max}$\\n\\n出射平行光束半径：$R_{out} = r_0'\\\\tan\\\\theta_{max}$\\n\\n横截面半径之比：$\\\\frac{R_{in}}{R_{out}} = \\\\frac{r_0}{r_0'}$\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 二、热力学问题\\n\\n已知：$l = 75.0\\\\ \\\\text{cm}$，$S = 10.0\\\\ \\\\text{cm}^2 = 1.00\\\\times10^{-3}\\\\ \\\\text{m}^2$\\n\\n$h = 25.0\\\\ \\\\text{cm} = 0.250\\\\ \\\\text{m}$，$T_0 = 400\\\\ \\\\text{K}$，$C_V = \\\\frac{5}{2}R$\\n\\n$\\\\rho = 13.6\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{kg/m}^3$，$p_0 = 75.0\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg}$，$g = 9.80\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}^2$\\n\\n初始状态：气柱高度$h_1 = h = 25.0\\\\ \\\\text{cm}$，水银柱高度$h_{Hg} = h = 25.0\\\\ \\\\text{cm}$\\n\\n封闭气体压强：$p_1 = p_0 + \\\\rho gh = 75.0\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg} + 25.0\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg} = 100\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg}$\\n\\n$p_1 = \\\\frac{100}{75}p_0 = \\\\frac{4}{3}p_0 = \\\\frac{4}{3}\\\\times1.013\\\\times10^5\\\\ \\\\text{Pa} = 1.35\\\\times10^5\\\\ \\\\text{Pa}$\\n\\n### （1）过程A\\n\\n水银上液面到达管口时，气柱高度$h_2 = l - h = 75.0 - 25.0 = 50.0\\\\ \\\\text{cm}$\\n\\n此过程为等压过程（水银柱高度不变，压强不变）。\\n\\n气体对外做功：$W_A = p_1\\\\Delta V = p_1 S(h_2 - h_1)$\\n\\n$W_A = 1.35\\\\times10^5 \\\\times 1.00\\\\times10^{-3} \\\\times (0.500 - 0.250)$\\n\\n$W_A = 1.35\\\\times10^5 \\\\times 1.00\\\\times10^{-3} \\\\times 0.250 = 33.8\\\\ \\\\text{J}$\\n\\n### （2）过程B\\n\\n继续加热至水银恰好全部流出，活塞到达管口。\\n\\n设某时刻水银柱高度为$x$（$x$从$h$减小到0），气柱高度为$l-x$。\\n\\n气体压强：$p(x) = p_0 + \\\\rho gx$\\n\\n气体体积：$V(x) = S(l-x)$\\n\\n由理想气体状态方程：$pV = nRT$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{p_1 V_1}{T_1} = \\\\frac{p_2 V_2}{T_2}$\\n\\n过程B初态（过程A末态）：$p_2 = p_1 = 100\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg}$，$V_2 = S(l-h) = 50.0S$，$T_2$待求\\n\\n由过程A等压：$\\\\frac{V_1}{T_1} = \\\\frac{V_2}{T_2}$，$\\\\frac{25.0S}{400} = \\\\frac{50.0S}{T_2}$\\n\\n$T_2 = 800\\\\ \\\\text{K}$\\n\\n过程B末态：$p_3 = p_0 = 75.0\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg}$，$V_3 = Sl = 75.0S$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{p_2 V_2}{T_2} = \\\\frac{p_3 V_3}{T_3}$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{100\\\\times50.0S}{800} = \\\\frac{75.0\\\\times75.0S}{T_3}$\\n\\n$T_3 = \\\\frac{75.0\\\\times75.0\\\\times800}{100\\\\times50.0} = 900\\\\ \\\\text{K}$\\n\\n判断过程B能否缓慢稳定发生：\\n\\n考虑准静态过程，气体压强需始终满足$p = p_0 + \\\\rho gx$。\\n\\n当水银逐渐流出时，$x$减小，$p$减小，$V$增大。\\n\\n由$pV = nRT$，$T = \\\\frac{pV}{nR} = \\\\frac{(p_0+\\\\rho gx)S(l-x)}{nR}$\\n\\n$T(x) = \\\\frac{S}{nR}(p_0 l - p_0 x + \\\\rho glx - \\\\rho gx^2)$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{dT}{dx} = \\\\frac{S}{nR}(-p_0 + \\\\rho gl - 2\\\\rho gx)$\\n\\n令$\\\\frac{dT}{dx} = 0$，得$x_m = \\\\frac{\\\\rho gl - p_0}{2\\\\rho g} = \\\\frac{l}{2} - \\\\frac{p_0}{2\\\\rho g}$\\n\\n$p_0 = 75.0\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg}$对应水银柱高75.0 cm，即$\\\\frac{p_0}{\\\\rho g} = 0.750\\\\ \\\\text{m}$\\n\\n$x_m = \\\\frac{0.750}{2} - \\\\frac{0.750}{2} = 0$\\n\\n在$x \\\\in [0, h]$范围内，$\\\\frac{dT}{dx} < 0$（当$x > 0$时），温度随$x$减小而升高。\\n\\n因此过程B可以缓慢稳定发生。\\n\\n过程B气体对外做功：\\n\\n$W_B = \\\\int_{V_2}^{V_3} p dV = \\\\int_{h}^{0} (p_0 + \\\\rho gx) \\\\cdot (-S dx) = S\\\\int_{0}^{h} (p_0 + \\\\rho gx) dx$\\n\\n$W_B = S\\\\left[p_0 h + \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\rho gh^2\\\\right] = p_0 Sh + \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\rho g h^2 S$\\n\\n$p_0 = 75.0\\\\ \\\\text{cmHg} = 1.013\\\\times10^5\\\\ \\\\text{Pa}$\\n\\n$W_B = 1.013\\\\times10^5 \\\\times 1.00\\\\times10^{-3} \\\\times 0.250 + \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\times13.6\\\\times10^3\\\\times9.80\\\\times0.250^2\\\\times1.00\\\\times10^{-3}$\\n\\n$W_B = 25.3 + 4.17 = 29.5\\\\ \\\\text{J}$\\n\\n气体内能变化：$\\\\Delta U_B = nC_V(T_3 - T_2)$\\n\\n物质的量：$n = \\\\frac{p_1 V_1}{RT_1} = \\\\frac{1.35\\\\times10^5 \\\\times 2.50\\\\times10^{-4}}{8.31\\\\times400} = 0.0101\\\\ \\\\text{mol}$\\n\\n$\\\\Delta U_B = 0.0101 \\\\times \\\\frac{5}{2} \\\\times 8.31 \\\\times (900 - 800) = 21.0\\\\ \\\\text{J}$\\n\\n由热力学第一定律：$Q_B = \\\\Delta U_B + W_B = 21.0 + 29.5 = 50.5\\\\ \\\\text{J}$\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 三、超球碰撞问题\\n\\n已知：$J = \\\\frac{2}{5}mr^2$，碰撞完全弹性，接触点无滑动。\\n\\n设碰撞前后球心水平速度为$v_x$、$v_x'$，角速度为$\\\\omega_z$、$\\\\omega_z'$。\\n\\n碰撞时接触点速度：$v_c = v_x + r\\\\omega_z$（向下碰撞）或$v_c = v_x - r\\\\omega_z$（向上碰撞）\\n\\n无滑动条件：碰撞后接触点速度反向，$v_c' = -v_c$\\n\\n动量定理：$m(v_x' - v_x) = \\\\int F_f dt = J_f$\\n\\n角动量定理：$J(\\\\omega_z' - \\\\omega_z) = r\\\\int F_f dt = rJ_f$（向下碰撞）或$J(\\\\omega_z' - \\\\omega_z) = -rJ_f$（向上碰撞）\\n\\n### （1）第1次碰撞（与下板）\\n\\n向下碰撞，接触点速度$v_c = v_{0x} + r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n无滑动：$v_{1x} + r\\\\omega_{1z} = -(v_{0x} + r\\\\omega_{0z})$\\n\\n动量：$m(v_{1x} - v_{0x}) = J_f$\\n\\n角动量：$\\\\frac{2}{5}mr^2(\\\\omega_{1z} - \\\\omega_{0z}) = rJ_f$\\n\\n消去$J_f$：$\\\\frac{2}{5}mr^2(\\\\omega_{1z} - \\\\omega_{0z}) = rm(v_{1x} - v_{0x})$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{2}{5}r(\\\\omega_{1z} - \\\\omega_{0z}) = v_{1x} - v_{0x}$\\n\\n联立$v_{1x} + r\\\\omega_{1z} = -v_{0x} - r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n由第二式：$r\\\\omega_{1z} = -v_{0x} - r\\\\omega_{0z} - v_{1x}$\\n\\n代入第一式：$\\\\frac{2}{5}(-v_{0x} - r\\\\omega_{0z} - v_{1x} - r\\\\omega_{0z}) = v_{1x} - v_{0x}$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{2}{5}(-v_{0x} - 2r\\\\omega_{0z} - v_{1x}) = v_{1x} - v_{0x}$\\n\\n$-2v_{0x} - 4r\\\\omega_{0z} - 2v_{1x} = 5v_{1x} - 5v_{0x}$\\n\\n$7v_{1x} = 3v_{0x} - 4r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$v_{1x} = \\\\frac{3}{7}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{4}{7}r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n代入求$\\\\omega_{1z}$：\\n\\n$r\\\\omega_{1z} = -v_{0x} - r\\\\omega_{0z} - \\\\frac{3}{7}v_{0x} + \\\\frac{4}{7}r\\\\omega_{0z} = -\\\\frac{10}{7}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{3}{7}r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{1z} = -\\\\frac{10}{7}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} - \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n### （2）第2次碰撞（与上板）\\n\\n向上碰撞，接触点速度$v_c = v_{1x} - r\\\\omega_{1z}$（注意符号）\\n\\n无滑动：$v_{2x} - r\\\\omega_{2z} = -(v_{1x} - r\\\\omega_{1z})$\\n\\n动量：$m(v_{2x} - v_{1x}) = J_f$\\n\\n角动量：$\\\\frac{2}{5}mr^2(\\\\omega_{2z} - \\\\omega_{1z}) = -rJ_f$\\n\\n消去$J_f$：$\\\\frac{2}{5}r(\\\\omega_{2z} - \\\\omega_{1z}) = -(v_{2x} - v_{1x})$\\n\\n联立$v_{2x} - r\\\\omega_{2z} = -v_{1x} + r\\\\omega_{1z}$\\n\\n解得：$v_{2x} = \\\\frac{3}{7}v_{1x} + \\\\frac{4}{7}r\\\\omega_{1z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{2z} = \\\\frac{10}{7}\\\\frac{v_{1x}}{r} - \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\omega_{1z}$\\n\\n代入$v_{1x}$、$\\\\omega_{1z}$：\\n\\n$v_{2x} = \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\left(\\\\frac{3}{7}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{4}{7}r\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right) + \\\\frac{4}{7}\\\\left(-\\\\frac{10}{7}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{3}{7}r\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right)$\\n\\n$v_{2x} = \\\\frac{9}{49}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{12}{49}r\\\\omega_{0z} - \\\\frac{40}{49}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{12}{49}r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$v_{2x} = -\\\\frac{31}{49}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{24}{49}r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{2z} = \\\\frac{10}{7r}\\\\left(\\\\frac{3}{7}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{4}{7}r\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right) - \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\left(-\\\\frac{10}{7}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} - \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right)$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{2z} = \\\\frac{30}{49}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} - \\\\frac{40}{49}\\\\omega_{0z} + \\\\frac{30}{49}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} + \\\\frac{9}{49}\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{2z} = \\\\frac{60}{49}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} - \\\\frac{31}{49}\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n### （3）第3次碰撞（与下板）\\n\\n向下碰撞，同理：\\n\\n$v_{3x} = \\\\frac{3}{7}v_{2x} - \\\\frac{4}{7}r\\\\omega_{2z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{3z} = -\\\\frac{10}{7}\\\\frac{v_{2x}}{r} - \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\omega_{2z}$\\n\\n代入$v_{2x}$、$\\\\omega_{2z}$：\\n\\n$v_{3x} = \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\left(-\\\\frac{31}{49}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{24}{49}r\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right) - \\\\frac{4}{7}\\\\left(\\\\frac{60}{49}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} - \\\\frac{31}{49}\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right)r$\\n\\n$v_{3x} = -\\\\frac{93}{343}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{72}{343}r\\\\omega_{0z} - \\\\frac{240}{343}v_{0x} + \\\\frac{124}{343}r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$v_{3x} = -\\\\frac{333}{343}v_{0x} + \\\\frac{52}{343}r\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{3z} = -\\\\frac{10}{7r}\\\\left(-\\\\frac{31}{49}v_{0x} - \\\\frac{24}{49}r\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right) - \\\\frac{3}{7}\\\\left(\\\\frac{60}{49}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} - \\\\frac{31}{49}\\\\omega_{0z}\\\\right)$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{3z} = \\\\frac{310}{343}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} + \\\\frac{240}{343}\\\\omega_{0z} - \\\\frac{180}{343}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} + \\\\frac{93}{343}\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{3z} = \\\\frac{130}{343}\\\\frac{v_{0x}}{r} + \\\\frac{333}{343}\\\\omega_{0z}$\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 四、磁偶极子问题\\n\\n### （1）相互作用势能\\n\\n磁针A在原点，磁矩$\\\\vec{\\\\mu}_A = \\\\mu\\\\hat{i}$。\\n\\n磁针B在$(0,0,z)$，磁矩$\\\\vec{\\\\mu}_B = \\\\mu(\\\\cos\\\\theta\\\\hat{i} + \\\\sin\\\\theta\\\\hat{k})$。\\n\\nA在B处产生的磁场：$\\\\vec{B}_A = \\\\frac{\\\\mu_0}{4\\\\pi z^3}[3(\\\\vec{\\\\mu}_A\\\\cdot\\\\hat{z})\\\\hat{z} - \\\\vec{\\\\mu}_A]$\\n\\n$\\\\vec{\\\\mu}_A\\\\cdot\\\\hat{z} = 0$，故$\\\\vec{B}_A = -\\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu}{4\\\\pi z^3}\\\\hat{i}$\\n\\n相互作用势能：$U = -\\\\vec{\\\\mu}_B\\\\cdot\\\\vec{B}_A = -\\\\mu(\\\\cos\\\\theta\\\\hat{i} + \\\\sin\\\\theta\\\\hat{k})\\\\cdot\\\\left(-\\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu}{4\\\\pi z^3}\\\\hat{i}\\\\right)$\\n\\n$U = \\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^3}\\\\cos\\\\theta$\\n\\n### （2）稳定平衡角度\\n\\n$z$不变，势能对$\\\\theta$求导：$\\\\frac{\\\\partial U}{\\\\partial\\\\theta} = -\\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^3}\\\\sin\\\\theta$\\n\\n平衡条件：$\\\\frac{\\\\partial U}{\\\\partial\\\\theta} = 0$，得$\\\\sin\\\\theta = 0$，$\\\\theta = 0$或$\\\\pi$。\\n\\n稳定性：$\\\\frac{\\\\partial^2 U}{\\\\partial\\\\theta^2} = -\\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^3}\\\\cos\\\\theta$\\n\\n$\\\\theta = 0$时，$\\\\frac{\\\\partial^2 U}{\\\\partial\\\\theta^2} = -\\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^3} < 0$，不稳定。\\n\\n$\\\\theta = \\\\pi$时，$\\\\frac{\\\\partial^2 U}{\\\\partial\\\\theta^2} = \\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^3} > 0$，稳定。\\n\\n稳定平衡角：$\\\\theta_{稳} = \\\\pi$\\n\\n### （3）受力平衡位置\\n\\n$\\\\theta = \\\\pi$时，$U = -\\\\frac{\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^3}$\\n\\nB受力：$F_z = -\\\\frac{\\\\partial U}{\\\\partial z} + mg = -\\\\frac{3\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^4} + mg$\\n\\n平衡条件：$F_z = 0$，$\\\\frac{3\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi z^4} = mg$\\n\\n$z_{eq} = \\\\left(\\\\frac{3\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{4\\\\pi mg}\\\\right)^{1/4}$\\n\\n稳定性分析：$\\\\frac{\\\\partial F_z}{\\\\partial z} = \\\\frac{3\\\\mu_0\\\\mu^2}{\\\\pi z^5} > 0$\\n\\n当$z$稍大于$z_{eq}$时，$F_z > 0$，B向下加速，远离平衡位置。\\n\\n当$z$稍小于$z_{eq}$时，$F_z < 0$，B向上加速，被A吸附。\\n\\n此平衡位置为不稳定平衡位置。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 五、原子激光制冷问题\\n\\n已知：$T = 350^\\\\circ\\\\text{C} = 623\\\\ \\\\text{K}$，$M = 40\\\\ \\\\text{u} = 40\\\\times1.66\\\\times10^{-27}\\\\ \\\\text{kg} = 6.64\\\\times10^{-26}\\\\ \\\\text{kg}$\\n\\n$\\\\Gamma = 5.00\\\\times10^6\\\\ \\\\text{s}^{-1}$，$\\\\lambda = 670\\\\ \\\\text{nm} = 6.70\\\\times10^{-7}\\\\ \\\\text{m}$\\n\\n$\\\\beta = -1.00\\\\times10^{10}\\\\ \\\\text{Hz/T}$，$h = 6.626\\\\times10^{-34}\\\\ \\\\text{J·s}$，$k_B = 1.38\\\\times10^{-23}\\\\ \\\\text{J/K}$\\n\\n### （1）方均根速率\\n\\n$v_0 = \\\\sqrt{\\\\frac{3k_B T}{M}} = \\\\sqrt{\\\\frac{3\\\\times1.38\\\\times10^{-23}\\\\times623}{6.64\\\\times10^{-26}}}$\\n\\n$v_0 = \\\\sqrt{\\\\frac{2.58\\\\times10^{-20}}{6.64\\\\times10^{-26}}} = \\\\sqrt{3.89\\\\times10^5} = 624\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}$\\n\\n### （2）减速加速度和距离\\n\\n每次散射原子获得动量变化：$\\\\Delta p = \\\\frac{h}{\\\\lambda}$\\n\\n加速度：$a = \\\\frac{\\\\Gamma h}{M\\\\lambda} = \\\\frac{5.00\\\\times10^6\\\\times6.626\\\\times10^{-34}}{6.64\\\\times10^{-26}\\\\times6.70\\\\times10^{-7}}$\\n\\n$a = \\\\frac{3.31\\\\times10^{-27}}{4.45\\\\times10^{-32}} = 7.44\\\\times10^4\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}^2$\\n\\n减速距离：$d = \\\\frac{v_0^2}{2a} = \\\\frac{624^2}{2\\\\times7.44\\\\times10^4} = \\\\frac{3.89\\\\times10^5}{1.49\\\\times10^5} = 2.61\\\\ \\\\text{m}$\\n\\n### （3）多普勒频移\\n\\n激光频率需减小：$\\\\Delta f = \\\\frac{v_0}{\\\\lambda} = \\\\frac{624}{6.70\\\\times10^{-7}} = 9.31\\\\times10^8\\\\ \\\\text{Hz}$\\n\\n### （4）磁场分布\\n\\n原子速度$v(z)$满足：$v^2 = v_0^2 - 2az$\\n\\n多普勒频移：$\\\\Delta f_D = \\\\frac{v(z)}{\\\\lambda}$\\n\\n塞曼频移：$\\\\Delta f_Z = \\\\beta B(z)$\\n\\n共振条件：$\\\\Delta f_D + \\\\Delta f_Z = \\\\text{常数} = \\\\frac{v_0}{\\\\lambda}$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{v(z)}{\\\\lambda} + \\\\beta B(z) = \\\\frac{v_0}{\\\\lambda}$\\n\\n$B(z) = \\\\frac{v_0 - v(z)}{\\\\lambda|\\\\beta|} = \\\\frac{v_0 - \\\\sqrt{v_0^2 - 2az}}{\\\\lambda|\\\\beta|}$\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 六、带电圆筒问题\\n\\n### （1）电场强度\\n\\n由高斯定理，距离轴$r$处：\\n\\n$r < r_1$：$E = 0$\\n\\n$r_1 < r < r_2$：$E = \\\\frac{q}{2\\\\pi\\\\epsilon_0 r}$，方向沿径向向外\\n\\n$r > r_2$：$E = 0$\\n\\n### （2）磁感应强度\\n\\n圆筒旋转形成面电流，内筒面电流密度$K_1 = \\\\frac{q\\\\omega}{2\\\\pi}$，外筒$K_2 = -\\\\frac{q\\\\omega}{2\\\\pi}$。\\n\\n由安培环路定理：\\n\\n$r < r_1$：$B = 0$\\n\\n$r_1 < r < r_2$：$B = \\\\mu_0 K_1 = \\\\frac{\\\\mu_0 q\\\\omega}{2\\\\pi}$，方向沿轴向\\n\\n$r > r_2$：$B = 0$\\n\\n### （3）点电荷到达外筒条件\\n\\n点电荷在电磁场中运动，能量守恒：\\n\\n$\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\mu v_r^2 + \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\mu v_\\\\phi^2 + Q\\\\phi(r) = \\\\text{常数}$\\n\\n电势差：$\\\\phi(r_1) - \\\\phi(r_2) = \\\\int_{r_1}^{r_2} E dr = \\\\frac{q}{2\\\\pi\\\\epsilon_0}\\\\ln\\\\frac{r_2}{r_1}$\\n\\n点电荷从静止释放，初始动能为0。\\n\\n到达外筒需满足：$Q[\\\\phi(r_1) - \\\\phi(r_2)] \\\\geq 0$\\n\\n由于$Q$与$q$同号，$\\\\phi(r_1) > \\\\phi(r_2)$，电势能减少，动能增加。\\n\\n点电荷总能到达外筒，与$\\\\omega$无关。\\n\\n### （4）外圆筒加速过程\\n\\n#### （i）内圆筒角速度\\n\\n系统角动量守恒（不计外力矩时），但此处有外力矩。\\n\\n考虑电磁感应，外筒旋转产生磁场变化，在内筒感应电动势。\\n\\n由对称性和角动量守恒（电磁场+机械）：\\n\\n$m r_1^2\\\\omega + m r_2^2\\\\Omega = 0$（初始总角动量为0）\\n\\n$\\\\omega = -\\\\frac{r_2^2}{r_1^2}\\\\Omega$\\n\\n#### （ii）外力矩冲量矩\\n\\n$J = \\\\int M dt = \\\\Delta L_{机械} = m r_2^2\\\\Omega + m r_1^2\\\\omega = m r_2^2\\\\Omega - m r_2^2\\\\Omega = 0$\\n\\n#### （iii）总机械角动量\\n\\n$L = m r_1^2\\\\omega + m r_2^2\\\\Omega = 0$\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 七、汽车力学模型\\n\\n已知：$M = 1.8\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{kg}$，$h = 0.1\\\\ \\\\text{m}$，$r = 0.40\\\\ \\\\text{m}$，$L = 2.9\\\\ \\\\text{m}$\\n\\n$\\\\tau = 4.0\\\\times10^2\\\\ \\\\text{N·m}$，$ir = 10$，$g = 9.8\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}^2$\\n\\n### （1）正压力和安全加速度\\n\\n对汽车整体，沿斜面方向：$(M+2m)a = F_{前} + F_{后} - (M+2m)g\\\\sin\\\\theta$\\n\\n垂直斜面方向：$N_{前} + N_{后} = (M+2m)g\\\\cos\\\\theta$\\n\\n对质心力矩平衡（无转动）：$N_{后}\\\\cdot\\\\frac{L}{2} - N_{前}\\\\cdot\\\\frac{L}{2} - (F_{前}+F_{后})h = 0$\\n\\n$(N_{后} - N_{前})\\\\frac{L}{2} = (F_{前}+F_{后})h = (M+2m)(a + g\\\\sin\\\\theta)h$\\n\\n$N_{后} - N_{前} = \\\\frac{2(M+2m)(a + g\\\\sin\\\\theta)h}{L}$\\n\\n联立$N_{前} + N_{后} = (M+2m)g\\\\cos\\\\theta$\\n\\n$2N_{后} = (M+2m)g\\\\cos\\\\theta + \\\\frac{2(M+2m)(a + g\\\\sin\\\\theta)h}{L}$\\n\\n$N_{后} = \\\\frac{M+2m}{2}\\\\left[g\\\\cos\\\\theta + \\\\frac{2(a + g\\\\sin\\\\theta)h}{L}\\\\right]$\\n\\n$N_{前} = \\\\frac{M+2m}{2}\\\\left[g\\\\cos\\\\theta - \\\\frac{2(a + g\\\\sin\\\\theta)h}{L}\\\\right]$\\n\\n前轮不离开地面条件：$N_{前} > 0$\\n\\n$g\\\\cos\\\\theta > \\\\frac{2(a + g\\\\sin\\\\theta)h}{L}$\\n\\n$a < \\\\frac{gL\\\\cos\\\\theta}{2h} - g\\\\sin\\\\theta$\\n\\n$a_{安全} = g\\\\left(\\\\frac{L\\\\cos\\\\theta}{2h} - \\\\sin\\\\theta\\\\right)$\\n\\n### （2）车身加速度\\n\\n后轮受力矩$\\\\tau_{轮}$，摩擦力$F_{后} = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{r}$\\n\\n整体：$(M+2m)a = F_{后} - (M+2m)g\\\\sin\\\\theta = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{r} - (M+2m)g\\\\sin\\\\theta$\\n\\n$a = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{r(M+2m)} - g\\\\sin\\\\theta$\\n\\n### （3）最大加速度和最小摩擦系数\\n\\n$m \\\\ll M$，近似$M+2m \\\\approx M$。\\n\\n电机最大力矩$\\\\tau_{轮} = ir\\\\cdot\\\\tau = 10\\\\times4.0\\\\times10^2 = 4.0\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{N·m}$\\n\\n水平地面（$\\\\theta = 0$）：\\n\\n$a(0^\\\\circ) = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{rM} = \\\\frac{4.0\\\\times10^3}{0.40\\\\times1.8\\\\times10^3} = 5.6\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}^2$\\n\\n30度上坡（$\\\\theta = 30^\\\\circ$）：\\n\\n$a(30^\\\\circ) = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{rM} - g\\\\sin30^\\\\circ = 5.6 - 9.8\\\\times0.5 = 0.70\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}^2$\\n\\n最小摩擦系数：\\n\\n不滑动条件：$F_{后} \\\\leq \\\\mu N_{后}$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{r} \\\\leq \\\\mu N_{后}$\\n\\n水平地面：$N_{后} \\\\approx \\\\frac{Mg}{2} + \\\\frac{Mah}{L} = \\\\frac{1.8\\\\times10^3\\\\times9.8}{2} + \\\\frac{1.8\\\\times10^3\\\\times5.6\\\\times0.1}{2.9}$\\n\\n$N_{后} = 8.82\\\\times10^3 + 3.48\\\\times10^2 = 9.17\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{N}$\\n\\n$\\\\mu_{min}(0^\\\\circ) = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{轮}}{rN_{后}} = \\\\frac{4.0\\\\times10^3}{0.40\\\\times9.17\\\\times10^3} = 1.1$\\n\\n30度上坡：$N_{后} = \\\\frac{Mg\\\\cos30^\\\\circ}{2} + \\\\frac{M(a+g\\\\sin30^\\\\circ)h}{L}$\\n\\n$N_{后} = \\\\frac{1.8\\\\times10^3\\\\times9.8\\\\times0.866}{2} + \\\\frac{1.8\\\\times10^3\\\\times(0.70+4.9)\\\\times0.1}{2.9}$\\n\\n$N_{后} = 7.64\\\\times10^3 + 3.48\\\\times10^2 = 7.99\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{N}$\\n\\n$\\\\mu_{min}(30^\\\\circ) = \\\\frac{4.0\\\\times10^3}{0.40\\\\times7.99\\\\times10^3} = 1.3$\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 八、电动汽车电机问题\\n\\n### （1）电机特性\\n\\n反电动势：$\\\\mathcal{E} = Blv = Bl r_{线圈}\\\\omega$\\n\\n电流：$I = \\\\frac{V - \\\\mathcal{E}}{R_{线圈} + R_{内}} = \\\\frac{V - Bl r_{线圈}\\\\omega}{R_{总}}$\\n\\n输出力矩：$\\\\tau = BIl = \\\\frac{Bl(V - Bl r_{线圈}\\\\omega)}{R_{总}}$\\n\\n$\\\\tau(\\\\omega) = \\\\frac{BlV}{R_{总}} - \\\\frac{B^2l^2 r_{线圈}}{R_{总}}\\\\omega$\\n\\n最大力矩（$\\\\omega = 0$）：$\\\\tau_{max} = \\\\frac{BlV}{R_{总}}$\\n\\n最大转速（$\\\\tau = 0$）：$\\\\omega_{max} = \\\\frac{V}{Bl r_{线圈}}$\\n\\n输出功率：$P = \\\\tau\\\\omega = \\\\frac{BlV\\\\omega}{R_{总}} - \\\\frac{B^2l^2 r_{线圈}\\\\omega^2}{R_{总}}$\\n\\n最大功率：$P_{max} = \\\\frac{\\\\tau_{max}\\\\omega_{max}}{4} = \\\\frac{BlV}{R_{总}}\\\\cdot\\\\frac{V}{Bl r_{线圈}}\\\\cdot\\\\frac{1}{4} = \\\\frac{V^2}{4R_{总} r_{线圈}}$\\n\\n用$\\\\tau_{max}$、$\\\\omega_{max}$、$P_{max}$表示：\\n\\n$\\\\tau(\\\\omega) = \\\\tau_{max}\\\\left(1 - \\\\frac{\\\\omega}{\\\\omega_{max}}\\\\right)$\\n\\n### （2）车速与时间关系\\n\\n$a = \\\\frac{r\\\\tau_{轮}}{3(M+m)}$，$\\\\tau_{轮} = ir\\\\cdot\\\\tau_{电机}$\\n\\n$\\\\tau_{电机} = \\\\tau_{max}\\\\left(1 - \\\\frac{ir\\\\cdot v/r}{\\\\omega_{max}}\\\\right) = \\\\tau_{max}\\\\left(1 - \\\\frac{ir\\\\cdot v}{r\\\\omega_{max}}\\\\right)$\\n\\n$a = \\\\frac{dv}{dt} = \\\\frac{r\\\\cdot ir\\\\cdot\\\\tau_{max}}{3(M+m)}\\\\left(1 - \\\\frac{ir\\\\cdot v}{r\\\\omega_{max}}\\\\right)$\\n\\n令$A = \\\\frac{ir^2\\\\tau_{max}}{3(M+m)}$，$B = \\\\frac{ir}{r\\\\omega_{max}}$\\n\\n$\\\\frac{dv}{dt} = A(1 - Bv)$\\n\\n$\\\\int_0^v \\\\frac{dv'}{1 - Bv'} = \\\\int_0^t A dt'$\\n\\n$-\\\\frac{1}{B}\\\\ln(1 - Bv) = At$\\n\\n$v(t) = \\\\frac{1}{B}(1 - e^{-ABt}) = \\\\frac{r\\\\omega_{max}}{ir}\\\\left(1 - e^{-\\\\frac{ir^2\\\\tau_{max}}{3(M+m)}\\\\cdot\\\\frac{ir}{r\\\\omega_{max}}t}\\\\right)$\\n\\n$v(t) = \\\\frac{r\\\\omega_{max}}{ir}\\\\left(1 - e^{-\\\\frac{i^2r\\\\tau_{max}}{3(M+m)\\\\omega_{max}}t}\\\\right)$\\n\\n### （3）加速时间和能量\\n\\n$v_f = 100\\\\ \\\\text{km/h} = 27.8\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}$\\n\\n$P_{max} = 2.0\\\\times10^2\\\\ \\\\text{kW} = 2.0\\\\times10^5\\\\ \\\\text{W}$\\n\\n$\\\\tau_{max} = 4.0\\\\times10^2\\\\ \\\\text{N·m}$\\n\\n$\\\\omega_{max} = \\\\frac{4P_{max}}{\\\\tau_{max}} = \\\\frac{4\\\\times2.0\\\\times10^5}{4.0\\\\times10^2} = 2.0\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{rad/s}$\\n\\n$m \\\\ll M$，$3(M+m) \\\\approx 3M = 5.4\\\\times10^3\\\\ \\\\text{kg}$\\n\\n时间常数：$\\\\alpha = \\\\frac{i^2r\\\\tau_{max}}{3M\\\\omega_{max}} = \\\\frac{100\\\\times0.40\\\\times4.0\\\\times10^2}{5.4\\\\times10^3\\\\times2.0\\\\times10^3} = 1.48\\\\times10^{-3}\\\\ \\\\text{s}^{-1}$\\n\\n终值速度：$v_{终} = \\\\frac{r\\\\omega_{max}}{ir} = \\\\frac{0.40\\\\times2.0\\\\times10^3}{10} = 80\\\\ \\\\text{m/s}$\\n\\n$v_f = v_{终}(1 - e^{-\\\\alpha t})$\\n\\n$27.8 = 80(1 - e^{-1.48\\\\times10^{-3}t})$\\n\\n$e^{-1.48\\\\times10^{-3}t} = 1 - \\\\frac{27.8}{80} = 0.653$\\n\\n$t = -\\\\frac{\\\\ln 0.653}{1.48\\\\times10^{-3}} = 287\\\\ \\\\text{s} \\\\approx 2.9\\\\times10^2\\\\ \\\\text{s}$\\n\\n消耗电池能量：\\n\\n$E_{电池} = \\\\int_0^t P_{输入} dt = \\\\int_0^t \\\\frac{V^2}{R_{总}}\\\\left(1 - \\\\frac{\\\\omega}{\\\\omega_{max}}\\\\right) dt$\\n\\n机械能增量：$\\\\Delta E_{机械} = \\\\frac{1}{2}Mv_f^2 = \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\times1.8\\\\times10^3\\\\times27.8^2 = 6.96\\\\times10^5\\\\ \\\\text{J} = 0.193\\\\ \\\\text{kWh}$\\n\\n效率：$\\\\eta = \\\\frac{\\\\Delta E_{机械}}{E_{电池}}$\\n\\n在恒功率近似下，$E_{电池} \\\\approx P_{max} t = 2.0\\\\times10^5\\\\times287 = 5.74\\\\times10^7\\\\ \\\\text{J} = 16\\\\ \\\\text{kWh}$\\n\\n$\\\\eta = \\\\frac{0.193}{16} = 1.2\\\\%$\\n\\n（注：实际效率应考虑电机效率曲线，此处为简化估算）\"}"
